    "title": "問題児たちの王",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "トレーニング前、少し早めにコースへ着くと\r\n勇ましい声が聞こえてきた。",
            "enText": "I arrived at the course a little \nearly before the training and I \ncould hear the brave voices.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 6680334317046508959
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -4932521650017977476
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7629746770165394815,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "――さあ走れ！\r\n止まるな、脚を動かせ！",
            "enText": "—Come on, run! Don't stop, move your legs!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 2073258899361132486
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 2544043023658958017
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8685213567340215333,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスの取り巻き",
            "enName": "Siruis Follower",
            "jpText": "はぁ、はぁ……！\r\nよっしゃあ、先輩！　タイム更新ですっ！",
            "enText": "Haa, haa…! Yay, senpai! My time improved!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": 8995154735688085723
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 3603713312353231867
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3511303787085622179,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "ハハッ、言った通りだろ？　踏み込み\r\nすぎるな、脚の回転を意識しろってな。",
            "enText": "Ha ha, I told you, didn't I? Don't \nover-step, and be aware of the \nrotation of your legs.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -4556298657523107495
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 8894215277464156060
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5028826316690742098,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シリウスシンボリが大勢の生徒に指示を\r\n出している。その姿は教官さながらに\n頼もしいが――",
            "enText": "Sirius Simboli is giving instructions to a \nlarge group of students. She looks like a \ngood teacher, but—",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -8100477578981459345
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": 1655419795227899528
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3519559126607581316,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "気弱なウマ娘",
            "enName": "Timid Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "うわぁ、どうしよう……\r\nシリウス先輩と取り巻きの不良たちだ……！",
            "enText": "Wow, what to do… It's Sirius senior and her \ncronies, the delinquents…!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": 3975799022807549342
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": 1530857716961784611
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2555699969386660336,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "真面目なウマ娘",
            "enName": "Serious Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "困りましたね。これでは\r\nトレーニングをする場所が……。",
            "enText": "I'm in trouble. This means that \nthe place to train is…",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "pathId": -5016407750323479756,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あたりを見回すと、コース外の\r\n生徒はみな困った顔をしている。\nどういうことだろう……？",
            "enText": "When I look around, I see that all the \nstudents outside the course have a confused \nlook on their faces. What's going on here…?",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "pathId": 5472484421391434969,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "シリウス先輩、少々よろしいですか。",
            "enText": "Sirius, may I have a word with you?",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 141,
                    "pathId": -897377461001831058
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -971738899599623687
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 157,
                    "pathId": 3066835828071709881
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 145,
                    "pathId": -9190785203155867153
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4578594514341619585,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "……あぁ？",
            "enText": "… What?",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 12,
                    "pathId": -1405715718519913311
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -1479197804963656373
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 5894114628332326651
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 5001695350344192731
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7704629050107939044,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "大勢の者を従え、不当にコースを\r\n占拠していると生徒会に訴えが来ております。",
            "enText": "A complaint has been made to the student \ncouncil that you are unfairly occupying the \ncourse with a large number of people.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": 4705171327697903119
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 6934379997779197714
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": -2749688573783183375
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -8332415597526403720
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7898425674791057765,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "つきましては、他の生徒に支障が出ぬよう\r\n場所を空けてはいただけませんか。",
            "enText": "We would appreciate it if you could \ngive us some space so that other \nstudents are not disturbed.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -7063056286266314313
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -1033877864005316028
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": -7034388446959725804
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 5924855362996793777
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3855836180309313391,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "嫌だね。",
            "enText": "I don't think so.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 50,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -913410185218828668
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -5500132684307744219
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -1149600461901605015
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 8238940730833059221
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4400848199599690327,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "見ろよ、コイツらの顔。\r\n……な、わかるだろ？",
            "enText": "Look at their mugs… you know what I mean?",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -1524797225743458851
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": -1067618053063019172
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 5961126200899398295
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": 3583065535125428390
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1789005317368685610,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "全員、門限破りに校則破り。\r\n毎回バカみたいに反省文書かされて、\nろくにトレーニングする余裕もない。",
            "enText": "They break the curfew, the school rules. They \nhave to write a stupid sorry letter every \ntime, not giving them legit time to train.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 5853199426185680613
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": -1613514655467171961
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 1296090265020578470
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 2036622270671272382
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7488142443868872157,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "だから私が見てやってる。\r\nこうして、場所と時間を確保してな。",
            "enText": "That's why I'm looking after them. This way, \nI have a place and a time.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": -8508893512599363724
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 3946750749888288875
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 978068454991114502
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 7265905895108466771
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8232521047902642599,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "ですが……それは規則を破ったがゆえ。\r\n規則の遵守を徹底せねば、\n学園の運営は立ち行きません。",
            "enText": "But… is not the same as breaking the rules. \nIf we don't follow the rules, we won't be \nable to run the school.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 5050414489077598625
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 865029523331032685
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": -2882098722440867382
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": -2969223650198779935
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2463680127945534007,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "じゃ、規則のためならコイツらは\r\n締め出されてもいいって？",
            "enText": "So they're willing to be locked \nout for the sake of the rules?",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -3836714108605737878
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 5936013169301960355
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 7446708268492456106
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -8380724140046793785
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1417762856306490313,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "ハッ、私はそうは思わねぇな。",
            "enText": "Ha, I don't think so.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": -1062796872837319688
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -3794068096694158429
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -336744084970820894
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -1910410835599986373
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9093776611920962972,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "この学園は、なんでもかんでも順番待ち。\r\nそして1度規則を破ったら最後、\nどんどん後回しにされていく。",
            "enText": "In this school, everything is a waiting \ngame. And once you break a rule, you're put \non the back burner.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": -1480453060455424906
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": 7406970144357288135
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": 3484688118066567828
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": -1898113908757945958
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8611324028273428342,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "どうにもならねぇ事情があって\r\n仕方なく規則を破っていようと、\nお構いなく、だ。",
            "enText": "I don't care if you're breaking \nthe rules because you've got to, \nbecause you've got to.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "pathId": 3162712811657386701,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "つまりな、個人の事情は全無視なのが\r\nこの学園の『規則』。",
            "enText": "In other words, the school's \"rules\" ignore \nall personal circumstances.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -8140729641043341881
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": -844267972362689583
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 174,
                    "pathId": 7908388664553119443
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 173,
                    "pathId": 6835251577780340069
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -576608520649922430,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "そして『規則』通りやってりゃ、コイツら\r\n全員終わってるってワケだ。――そうだろ？",
            "enText": "And if they'd done it by the book, they'd \nall be finished. —Aren't they?",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 934949985834621268
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -5068228770122121780
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -1567726522646257315
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -1904107938651572350
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8276569227850072379,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "それは――",
            "enText": "It is—",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -7197176306419016201
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 7640397944399525981
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -9006255588466332712
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -5636143540739134245
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5506294527381756437,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "それと、もう1つ。さっき\r\n生徒会に訴えが来てるって言ったよな。",
            "enText": "And one more thing. Earlier, you said there \nwas an appeal to the student council.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": -8547062672234824168
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -1947883315872367797
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -849181633786732159
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 3336102562697071809
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -710678010512244386,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "ならそっちの王様はどうしたよ？\r\n話があるならアイツが直々に来るべきだろ。",
            "enText": "Then what about your king? If she wants to \ntalk, she should come in person.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": -6186105577199005285
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -4148101152253039677
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -5707950204747910343
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -4072813256188363586
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2965648928608390717,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "いい機会だ、伝えとけ。\r\nいつまでも高みの見物してるなら、\nこっちも聞く耳持たねぇってな。",
            "enText": "This is your chance to tell her. If you keep \nlooking down your nose at me, I'm not going \nto listen to you.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": -8990019382502733926
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -808980211771293055
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -6615841935133003786
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": 2898213023273652376
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2252809843449780259,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "――おいお前ら、続けるぞ！\r\n走れ！　前へ進め！！",
            "enText": "—Hey you guys, let's keep going! \nRun! Keep moving forward!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": 4782934436138523398
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 17,
                    "pathId": -5821707947539262253
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": 8941964290681111010
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -5768943574459407734
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3081842643515916231,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シリウスシンボリは生徒たちへの指示を\r\n再開した。問題児っぷりを発揮しつつ、\nその姿はどこか頼もしくも見えた。",
            "enText": "Sirius Simboli resumed her instructions to \nthe students. Sirius Simboli was back in \ncharge of the students.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 116,
            "pathId": -3534283823514339535,
            "blockIdx": 29
        }
    ],
